  "details": "The module doesn't sufficiently sanitize customer comments in the order receipt email template; this could be exploited to achieve Cross-site Scripting (XSS).\n\nThis vulnerability is mitigated by the fact that it only affects installations with Checkout (`commerce_checkout`) enabled, and the \"Comments\" checkout pane (id: `customer_comments`) is explicitly used, which is disabled by default.",
